Information will always &quot;trickle&quot; down. It's only a matter of time that is the issue. People who are resistant to the inevitability of it will come off looking like grumpy old men who in their day, walked to school in the snow, with no shoes, uphill, both ways. Such is the penalty for having the benefit of being able to say you were &quot;first&quot;.<br>
<br>
In the mean time, those of us who come later and aren't as well geared or experienced will try to take the bus and even in taking the bus, will still hit roadblocks on occasion. <p><table width=100%><tr><td width=33%><font color=blue><i><b>Sage Svenuce Summonstuff</b></i></font><br>
